cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with machine vision systems and learning new visual concepts from few examples, which are topics typically covered in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also mentions meta-learning, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Finally, the paper uses a hallucinator to produce additional training examples, which could be related to neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
